     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="1"/>
   <head>The Author to the Reader.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>If thou dost read or hear this work,</l>
      <l>Onely see thou doe this,</l>
      <l>Haue care to mend thy euill wayes,</l>
      <l>Now past and done amisse.</l>
      <l>All those that still presume in sin,</l>
      <l>Not minding to amend,</l>
      <l>Dayly this Booke will witnesse be</l>
      <l>Reuengefull in the end.</l>
      <l>Each day repent, Oh still repent</l>
      <l>With speede, I humbly pray,</l>
      <l>Euen for his Sons sake, Iesus Christ,</l>
      <l>So sinne is washt away.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>Anagramma: Annon Iesu reades?</closer>
</div>
